pessulus 0.10.1
===============

  Features

	* New UI that uses a treeview to select the current page (Rob Bradford,
	  Vincent)

  Fixes

	* Open the new help with the help button (not for Sabayon) (Vincent)
	* Mark name and comment of the .desktop file as translatable (Vincent)
	* Remove line feeds and extra spacing from tooltips generated from the
	  schemas (Dennis Cranston)
	* Do not set initial visibility of dialog to true, so the dialog will
	  open centered properly (Dennis Cranston)
	* HIG fixes (Dennis Cranston)
	* Use po/LINGUAS (Brian Pepple)

  Translators

	* Alexander Shopov (bg)
	* josep (ca)
	* Lukáš Novotný (cs)
	* Rhys Jones (cy)
	* Kostas Papadimas (el)
	* Francisco Javier F. Serrador (es)
