pessulus 0.2
============

  Features

	* simplify the "safe protocols" edition (Vincent)
	* new UI for fine-grained lockdown
	* integration with sabayon (Vincent, Alexander Larsson)

  Fixes

	* set sensitivity of the "safe protocols" widgets at startup (Vincent)
	* HIG fixes (Dennis Cranston)
	* works with python 2.3 (Benoît Dejean)
	* rename Web Browser tab to Epiphany Web Browser (Vincent)
	* code fixes (Vincent)

  Translators

	* Adam Weinberger (en_CA)
	* Francisco Javier F. Serrador (es)
	* Takeshi AIHANA (ja)
	* Guilherme de S. Pastore (pt_BR)
